013package org.apache.juneau.http.part;
014
015import org.apache.http.*;
016
017/**
018 * Identifies a class that can be converted to a {@link NameValuePair} object.
019 *
020 * <ul class='seealso'>
021 *    <li class='link'><a class="doclink" href="../../../../../overview-summary.html#juneau-rest-common">juneau-rest-common</a>
022 * </ul>
023 */
024public interface NameValuePairable {
025
026   /**
027    * Convert the object to a {@link NameValuePair}.
028    *
029    * @return The object converted to a {@link NameValuePair}.
030    */
031   NameValuePair asNameValuePair();
032}
